lru-type.name: LS
lru-type.description: One laser is considered as the reference laser or the Master Laser while a second one, the Slave Laser, is being Phase Locked to the reference laser in a subsystem called the Laser Synthesizer. Both Master Laser and Slave Laser signals are split in multiple outputs for amplification and distribution from the central building to the antennas via a fiber optic network reaching a distance up to 15 km.
